quran[22]{c,v,t,f}:
  54,50,"Àṣẹ Wa (fún mímú n̄ǹkan bẹ) kò tayọ (àṣẹ) ẹyọ kan ṣoṣo gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìṣẹ́jú.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, a máa lo ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ọdún nínú sàréè, àmọ́ láààrin ká ṣẹ́jú ká lajú, gbogbo ẹ̀dá máa jí dìde láti inú sàréè wọn."
  54,51,"Àti pé dájúdájú A ti pa àwọn irú yín rẹ́. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?",""
  54,52,"Gbogbo n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ sì wà nínú ìpín-ìpín tírà.",""
  54,53,"Àti pé gbogbo n̄ǹkan kékeré àti n̄ǹkan ńlá (tí wọ́n ṣe) wà ní àkọsílẹ̀.",""
  54,54,"Dájúdájú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) yóò wà nínú àwọn Ọgbà (Ìdẹ̀ra) pẹ̀lú àwọn odò (tó ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀).",""
  54,55,"Ní ibùjókòó òdodo nítòsí Ọba Alágbára Olùkápá.",""
  55,1,"Àjọkẹ́-ayé,",""
  55,2,"Ó fi ìmọ̀ al-Ƙur’ān mọ (ẹni tí Ó fẹ́).",""
  55,3,"Ó ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn.",""
  55,4,"Ó sì fi àlàyé (ọ̀rọ̀ sísọ) mọ̀ ọ́n.",""
  55,5,"Òòrùn àti òṣùpá (ń rìn) fún ìṣírò (ọjọ́ ayé).",""
  55,6,"Àwọn ìtàkùn ilẹ̀ àti igi ń forí kanlẹ̀ (fún Allāhu).",""
  55,7,"Àti sánmọ̀, Allāhu gbé e sókè. Ó sì fi òṣùwọ̀n òfin déédé lélẹ̀ (fún ẹ̀dá)",""
  55,8,"pé kí ẹ má ṣe tayọ ẹnu-ààlà níbi òṣùwọ̀n.",""
  55,9,"Ẹ gbé òṣùwọ̀n náà dúró pẹ̀lú dọ́gbadọ́gba. Kí ẹ sì má ṣe dín òṣùwọ̀n kù.",""
  55,10,"Ilẹ̀, (Allāhu) gbé e kalẹ̀ (sí abẹ́ sánmọ̀ fún àwọn ẹ̀dá.",""
  55,11,"Èso àti dàbínù alápó wà lórí (ilẹ̀).",""
  55,12,"Àti èso onípòpórò àti olóòórùn dídùn (wà lórí ilẹ̀).",""
  55,13,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?",""
  55,14,"(Allāhu) ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti ara amọ̀ gbígbẹ tó ń dún kokoko bí ìkòkò amọ̀.",""
  55,15,"Ó sì ṣẹ̀dá àlùjànnú láti ara ahọ́n iná tí kò ní èéfín.",""
  55,16,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?",""
